if 1 byte  |0|0000000
if 2 bytes |110|00000 then always next bytes |10|000000
if 3 bytes |1110|0000 (then |10|000000 |10|0000000)
|10|000000 |10|0000000)
if 4 bytes |11110|000 (then |10|000000 |10|000000 |10|0000000)

1 byte gives 7 total bits max
2 bytes gives 11 bits max
3 bytes gives 16 bits max
4 bytes gives 21 bits max

num limits hence
1 = 0 - 127
2 = 128 - 2047
3 = 2048 to 65535
4 = 65536 to 1,112,064
